Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.52,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,克里科特 解開了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:42.76,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 這也是魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:44.90,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:47.28,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.66,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,伙伴 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:50.09,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,又再一次 這樣認為了呢
Comment: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:31.92,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START--------/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是這個方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有獸鬼的殘留思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:38.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:40.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殘留?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:44.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那麼向卡思嘉她們使用念話怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:48.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也試著呼叫過好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:50.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但她們好像暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:51.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有銀之鎖子甲在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:57.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼就無法直接觸碰她們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:02.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個面孔是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:14.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,面孔?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是有可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是有些棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:23.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幽界的暗之領域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:24.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,克里科特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:27.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,通常是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幽界相現世會如此明顯的重疊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛看慣了 就感覺這裡不明所以的東東真是嗚嚷嗚嚷的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:38.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的深處就是獸鬼的巢穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺更不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我再試著呼喚她們一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:08.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 總算聯繫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過這裡到底是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣很不流通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐的氣突然混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是因為看到周圍的光景驚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:39.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們加快速度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要穿著銀之鎖子甲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:53.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐往上爬快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還算沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:08.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:16.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟會為了保護別人而揮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,待在那別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要引起獸鬼的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:56.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:10.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:11.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被獸鬼發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:14.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:16.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我來分散它們的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:22.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 怎麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱氣是魔法的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師都可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:32.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:36.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這招小偷要是學會了 很管用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我快暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好想趴在地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:57.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 待在我身後別動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:04.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身後的她的體溫不允許我這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一無所成的我第一次被人所託付
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比我還弱小的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那什麼都不懂 什麼也不知道的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不允許我這麼軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是報應 還是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他因為受傷動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,性命沒有大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我答應他要帶你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,依羅克村的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是來救你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:03.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:06.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救 是來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡還有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:10.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:14.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比襲擊村莊時還多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:18.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我來對付它們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們帶著村裡的人先走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以 再怎樣也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人對付那麼多 還沒有魔法的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:34.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:35.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞 因為你很多人獲救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:41.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:51.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,引燃圓彈上的導火線 數三下扔向敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:57.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你來殿後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:00.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,保護那些女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間囉嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:10.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在戰場是拿起武器 就算是孩子也是優秀的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被託付了就負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要做好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我就做給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是不要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷地冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,它們是蟑螂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 好久沒有的百人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:47.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是百頭斬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:55.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有一半馬上會成為餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 趕快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很準 沒想到挺適合對付它們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點 快站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:22.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:31.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:54.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,前方13隻 後方7隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能像剛才那樣引開它們的注意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能在這停下張開防護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有強行突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,前面的交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的就靠伊斯多洛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊7隻嗎  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:16.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間施放大型魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼有什麼可怕的東西一閃而過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:36.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要漲潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:12.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生 所有人都平安到達出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:14.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:22.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:22.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:28.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:29.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這回又怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:32.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生 這裡有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:38.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒化形了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:02.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到是獸鬼的內臟真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想你啊 男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:24.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我無論何時都能感覺到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在洞窟中 在塔裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:32.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在數不盡的夜晚 我都能感受到你的慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來 讓我更多感覺一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:39.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把一切都解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:48.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,毛骨悚然 很不好的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:55.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從洞穴底部吹來的異常氣息的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底 哪裡發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡慢吞吞的話 獸鬼們又要湧上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:03.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:07.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我要施展封鎖洞口的法術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯還在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:18.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不堵住的話 獸鬼們還會襲擊依羅克村和周邊村落的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯應該接到了我的念話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:27.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在法術發動之前 相信他能趕回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:39.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的靈魂和這個克里科特很相配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那種憎惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,苦悶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:54.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來 反抗給我看 抗爭之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:59.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用那又大又粗的東西 把我貫穿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,辦不到嗎 只是個人類的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就... ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上你自己嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像他一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:22.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在別人男歡女愛的時候不要來打擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你也想一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,國王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,胎海的娼姬斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受召喚而來的只有你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是自己來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來見他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:49.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,第五人出現就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:53.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經開始重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我也無話可說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡和我子宮內無異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大鬧一場吧 激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗的遺子們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 它們進不了這個圓陣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:17.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的農具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:25.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基說這個防壁對於不是幽體的東西無效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:26.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正合我意 來吧 你們這群猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:40.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在泥地裡漸漸下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在雨裡就是水的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在地上就是土的精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:51.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,按照萬物的原理法力是最有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但這同時也是危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:16:02.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果力量從施術者手失控 就有可能吞噬施術者本身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:08.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其中特別不能掉以輕心的就是黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:14.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,當你窺視深淵的時候 深淵也在窺視你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 國王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,玩的高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:30.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是黑暗的子宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是令人厭惡的靈魂凝結成形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,黃泉的湖畔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些東西要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像爬蟲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,機會 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好囉 這下拿著人類武器的就都收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好險 就剩最後一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:02.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:07.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,猴子老大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 用同伴當盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 要用這個解決它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,低點再低點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:43.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.96,0:18:01.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:05.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身體被撕裂的這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:11.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣完全 還要更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:16.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那把劍的話有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:22.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集成百上千的亡靈的怨念的那把劍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,貫穿她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:40.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爽 我的子官破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:42.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生和死都在子官中糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:46.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幹 幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,後會有期 可愛的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:19.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成功 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好大 嚇死人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是腐根之主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是腐爛樹木和淤泥的長者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遵從和這個小生命的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以爬在我身上的獸鬼為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使其全部化為蛆蟲的苗床
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,腐爛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:58.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就連格斯一起活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:08.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生趕緊跑出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 到底是哪裡發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙強行降臨和圓寂的餘波
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:20.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個領域內的生與死混在一起化為混沌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:24.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就這樣不管 不止是洞內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,連附近一帶都會吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前我們先完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,入口要被埋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡試斬也是無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:40.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了把他們全都葬送而吞食的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:45.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼 沒時間陪你玩奇術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:03.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把從使徒那裡搶來的貝黑萊特在我體內煉為刀刃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,名為喚水之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喚 水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:21.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:26.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 要塌了 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在努力中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:38.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要不行了 抑制不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:42.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:45.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:51.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,切開空間穿越異層
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是這把劍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:55.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又說些不知所謂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:21:59.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼從後面出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,又欠了人情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 史爾基
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:06.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:09.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個騎士是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:12.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.34,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.44,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 上啊
Comment: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:16.02,OPCht,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:23.88,OPCht,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:33.34,OPCht,,0,0,0,,任憑他人道長短  殊死之斗又何曾徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:43.68,OPCht,,0,0,0,,暗啞了的嘶吼  依舊在耳畔激盪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:49.93,OPCht,,0,0,0,,笑至盡頭之人不是我  亦無怨無悔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:53.84,OPCht,,0,0,0,,唯願能夠守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.48,OPCht,,0,0,0,,誅盡來敵戰至終
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:02.17,OPCht,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:07.11,OPCht,,0,0,0,,思思纏繞神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:11.63,OPCht,,0,0,0,,欲斷枷鎖魂難斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:17.41,OPCht,,0,0,0,,若能終結一切以戰止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.92,OPCht,,0,0,0,,焚盡我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:29.29,OPCht,,0,0,0,,困獸猶鬥  逆境之中尋生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:23.88,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:33.34,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:43.68,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:49.93,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:53.84,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.48,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:02.17,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:07.11,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:11.63,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:17.41,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.92,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:29.29,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:08.05,Preview,,0,0,0,,沒有搞錯 那是…使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:13.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,那是危險又強大的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:19.77,Preview,,0,0,0,,你說 鷹之團…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,那就更要泰然處之了
